{"tid":979222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【光速割蓆】華為解僱被波蘭安全部門拘捕員工　稱屬個人原因違法","createTime":"2019-01-12T14:11:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T16:34:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7ec8ff82adf6ef439ebeb340a712e98ea5989a","tid":979222,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T14:11:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1437770-20190112.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1437770-20190112.htm&d=HHoCLFOiTHifjI0VPSidX4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=8a075e3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1437770-20190112.htm&h=5fed5acf\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1437770-20190112.htm</a><br />\n華為宣布，解僱日前被波蘭安全部門拘捕的員工王偉晶。<br />\n<br />\n華為在聲明指出，波蘭代表處員工王偉晶因個人原因，涉嫌違反波蘭法律而被逮捕調查，由於事件對華為的全球聲譽，造成不良影響，依據合約相關管理規定，華為決定立刻終止與王偉晶的僱傭關係。<br />\n<br />\n聲明又強調，華為一直遵守業務所在國的所有適用法律法規，合規經營，並要求所有員工遵守所在國法律法規。"},{"pid":"f29e83cd32ed6418adce7cf2447dc1043b2ba6af","tid":979222,"uid":124526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"做得好"},{"pid":"a6417d5fd93028455ef3f4a8036a5508906bf708","tid":979222,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"未審就即切割, 應該斷正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82993cc12f93e76ae6faf7f19576e74ea6451814","tid":979222,"uid":83865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"切割左，為求保命，會唔會爆更多料"},{"pid":"8c1b233c2d06685a22e209b6a474150bb187ff38","tid":979222,"uid":61724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82993cc12f93e76ae6faf7f19576e74ea6451814","tid":979222,"uid":83865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"切割左，為求保命，會唔會爆更多料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"屋企人要唔要"}]}